213
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:00,720
Yakinlah,

214
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,790
lantai eksekutif kami

215
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:03,790
akan dengan sepenuh hati melayani mereka.

216
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,800
Saya mempercayakan Anda pada mereka, tentu saja.

217
00:11:07,140 --> 00:11:07,780
Ngomong-ngomong,

218
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,000
adalah kamar presidensial
ditempati saat ini?

219
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,800
Kami punya tamu jangka panjang di salah satunya.

220
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,320
Tapi kamar presidensial lainnya

221
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,120
